  "article_text": "Iris’ Blessing calls out to citizens all over Galia. Riches, luck and fun are in everyone’s future and you’re not going to want to miss it! For the next six months, enjoy double XP weekends and monthly drawings worth over $30,000!\n\nDouble XP Weekends — The More You Play, the More You Earn!\n\nDue to popular demand, we’re bringing back double XP weekends! Mark your calendars for the below 6 weekends where you’ll be able to earn DOUBLE the Ink. Play in official gunplay and racing matches, and for every 100 XP, earn 1 Ink!\n\nDouble XP Weekends\n\nDouble XP Weekend #1 : October 24, 2025 — October 26, 2025\n\nDouble XP Weekend #2 : N ovember 28, 2025 — November 30, 2025\n\nDouble XP Weekend #3 : December 26, 2025 — December 28, 2025\n\nDouble XP Weekend #4 : January 23, 2026 — January 25, 2026\n\nDouble XP Weekend #5 : February 27, 2026 — March 1, 2026\n\nDouble XP Weekend #6 : March 27, 2026 — March 29, 2026\n\nEarning double XP in Star Atlas will soon tie directly into the z.ink airdrop, meaning during these weekends, you’ll earn double the XP, double the Ink, and double the z.ink!\n\n$30,000 in Rewards — Monthly Discord Drawings!\n\nEvery second Friday of the month, you’ll have a chance to turn in tickets earned from joining Discord community events! Whether it’s an Atlas Brew, an Economic Forum, or a Game Night, collect your ticket and submit it through our Discord bot for a chance to win your share of the monthly drawing! Keep an eye out for exclusive challenges and activities that will give out tickets as well!\n\nHow to Earn Tickets and Submit Them into the Monthly Drawing\n\nJoin community events like the Atlas Brew or Star Atlas Economic Forum\n\nAttendees will be given a code to submit into the Discord bot (Sola Qint)\n\nType /claim or head to the #sola-qint-bot channel to submit your code\n\nThe Discord bot (Sola Qint) will give you tickets\n\nYour tickets will auto submit into the monthly drawing\n\nWhat Loot Can We Earn?\n\nEach month will have over $5,000 in Star Atlas loot up for grabs!\n\nNovember 14 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Busan Thrill of Life\n\n1 Calico Shipit\n\n1 Opal Rayfam\n\n1 Pearce R6\n\nDecember 12 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Calico Shipit\n\n1 Opal Rayfam\n\n1 Ogrika Tursic\n\nJanuary 9 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Opal Rayfam\n\n1 Calico Medtech\n\n1 Ogrika Tursic\n\nFebruary 13 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Calico Medtech\n\n1 Ogrika Mik\n\n1 Calico ATS Enforcer\n\nMarch 13 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Busan Thrill of Life\n\n1 Calico Shipit\n\n1 Ogrika Mik\n\n1 Ogrika Tursic\n\nApril 10 Drawing\n\n10 Fimbul ECO Unibomba\n\n10 VZUS solos\n\n5 Fimbul Lowbie\n\n7 Crew Gold 5\n\n10 Crew Gold 1\n\n10 Crew Silver 5\n\n10 Crew Silver 1\n\n5 Crew Platinum 5\n\n5 Crew Platinum 1\n\n1 Busan Thrill of Life\n\n1 Calico Shipit\n\n1 Pearce R6\n\nJoin in on the action, only in Discord.gg/StarAtlas !\n\nABOUT STAR ATLAS\n\nStar Atlas is an immersive, high-fidelity, world-building space adventure and grand strategy MMO built in Unreal Engine 5 and sustained by a real, galactic marketplace and economy.\n\nBuilt as a fully decentralized universe leveraging state-of-the-art blockchain using the Solana protocol, Star Atlas allows players to own and define their story and experience, while interacting in a live, dynamic, community-focused and controlled economy. Empowering a sustainable ecosystem is about allowing true asset ownership, marketability, co-creation, and driving true utility in the Star Atlas universe.\n\nIn Star Atlas, you explore space and distant planets, build powerful fleets and assemble crew to navigate, mine, craft, even conquer, while participating in a global, borderless digital economy — ultimately putting the power fully in the hands of the people.\n\nFind out more about Star Atlas by visiting www.Staratlas.com and our marketplace at www.Playstaratlas.com .\n\nStar Atlas Unreal Engine game experience is also available to download and play on Epic Games Store — join our Discord to get game key access and be part of our thriving community! You can also participate in governance of the Star Atlas DAO .\n\nJoin the Star Atlas community on: Twitter | Discord | YouTube | Reddit | Medium | LinkedIn",
